{"text_id":141211,"tokens":["How"," to"," Treat"," Aller","gic"," Der","matitis"," in"," Dogs","\n\n","Aller","gic"," dermatitis",","," also"," known"," as"," a","topic"," dermatitis",","," is"," a"," condition"," that"," can"," cause"," your"," dog"," to"," itch"," and"," scratch"," constantly","."," It"," is"," caused"," by"," an"," allergic"," reaction"," to"," certain"," substances"," in"," the"," environment",","," such"," as"," pollen",","," dust"," mites",","," or"," fleas","."," If"," your"," dog"," is"," suffering"," from"," allergic"," dermatitis",","," there"," are"," several"," ways"," you"," can"," treat"," it","."," In"," this"," article",","," we"," will"," explore"," some"," of"," the"," most"," effective"," methods"," for"," treating"," this"," condition",".","\n\n","Schedule"," a"," Blood"," Test"," for"," Your"," Dog","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," first"," things"," you"," should"," do"," if"," your"," dog"," is"," suffering"," from"," allergic"," dermatitis"," is"," to"," schedule"," a"," blood"," test","."," During"," a"," blood"," test",","," your"," vet"," will"," take"," a"," small"," sample"," of"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," blood"," and"," test"," it"," for"," allergens","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," identify"," what"," is"," causing"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," allergic"," reaction",","," so"," you"," can"," take"," steps"," to"," avoid"," it",".","\n\n","Talk"," to"," Your"," Vet"," About"," Getting"," an"," Intra","dermal"," Skin"," Test"," Done"," for"," Your"," Dog","\n\n","Another"," option"," for"," identifying"," allergens"," is"," to"," have"," an"," intra","dermal"," skin"," test"," done","."," This"," involves"," injecting"," a"," small"," amount"," of"," allergens"," into"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," skin"," and"," observing"," the"," reaction","."," This"," test"," is"," more"," accurate"," than"," a"," blood"," test",","," but"," it"," is"," more"," invasive"," and"," expensive",".","\n\n","Understand"," That"," Allergy"," Testing"," Can"," Improve"," the"," Quality"," of"," Your"," Dog","\u2019","s"," Life","\n\n","While"," allergy"," testing"," can"," be"," expensive",","," it"," can"," also"," greatly"," improve"," the"," quality"," of"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," life","."," By"," identifying"," the"," allergens"," that"," are"," causing"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," allergic"," dermatitis",","," you"," can"," take"," steps"," to"," remove"," them"," from"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," environment"," and"," reduce"," their"," symptoms",".","\n\n","Remove"," the"," Aller","gens"," From"," Your"," Home"," If"," You"," Can","\n\n","Once"," you"," have"," identified"," the"," allergens"," that"," are"," causing"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," allergic"," dermatitis",","," you"," should"," take"," steps"," to"," remove"," them"," from"," your"," home"," if"," you"," can","."," For"," example",","," if"," your"," dog"," is"," allergic"," to"," dust"," mites",","," you"," should"," make"," sure"," to"," vacuum"," your"," home"," regularly"," and"," wash"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," bedding"," frequently",".","\n\n","Wash"," Your"," Dog"," With"," Medic","ated"," Sham","po","os","\n\n","Another"," way"," to"," reduce"," the"," symptoms"," of"," allergic"," dermatitis"," is"," to"," wash"," your"," dog"," with"," medic","ated"," shampo","os","."," These"," shampo","os"," can"," help"," soothe"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," skin"," and"," reduce"," the"," inflammation"," caused"," by"," the"," allergic"," reaction",".","\n\n","Give"," Your"," Dog"," Anti","hist","amines","\n\n","Anti","hist","amines"," are"," another"," effective"," way"," to"," reduce"," the"," symptoms"," of"," allergic"," dermatitis"," in"," dogs","."," These"," medications"," can"," help"," reduce"," the"," itching",","," redness",","," and"," swelling"," associated"," with"," allergic"," reactions",".","\n\n","Talk"," to"," Your"," Vet"," About"," Getting"," Your"," Dog"," Systemic"," Anti","microb","ials","\n\n","In"," some"," cases",","," allergic"," dermatitis"," can"," lead"," to"," skin"," infections","."," If"," your"," dog"," has"," a"," skin"," infection",","," your"," vet"," may"," prescribe"," systemic"," anti","microb","ials"," to"," help"," treat"," it","."," These"," medications"," are"," usually"," given"," orally"," and"," can"," help"," clear"," up"," the"," infection",".","\n\n","Consider"," Getting"," Your"," Dog"," Immun","otherapy"," for"," Long","-","Term"," Treatment","\n\n","Immun","otherapy"," is"," a"," long","-","term"," treatment"," for"," allergic"," dermatitis"," that"," involves"," gradually"," exposing"," your"," dog"," to"," small"," amounts"," of"," the"," allergen"," over"," time","."," This"," can"," help"," your"," dog"," develop"," a"," tolerance"," to"," the"," allergen"," and"," reduce"," their"," symptoms"," over"," time",".","\n\n","Understand"," That"," Your"," Dog"," Can"," Develop"," Allergies"," to"," a"," Certain"," Food"," Over"," Time",","," Even"," If"," He","\u2019","s"," Been"," Eating"," the"," Food"," for"," Years","\n\n","It","\u2019","s"," important"," to"," understand"," that"," your"," dog"," can"," develop"," allergies"," to"," a"," certain"," food"," over"," time",","," even"," if"," they"," have"," been"," eating"," the"," food"," for"," years","."," If"," you"," suspect"," that"," your"," dog"," may"," be"," allergic"," to"," their"," food",","," you"," should"," talk"," to"," your"," vet"," about"," changing"," their"," diet",".","\n\n","Give"," Your"," Dog"," New"," Types"," of"," Protein","\n\n","If"," your"," dog"," is"," allergic"," to"," a"," certain"," protein"," source",","," such"," as"," chicken"," or"," beef",","," you"," may"," need"," to"," experiment"," with"," other"," protein"," sources","."," For"," example",","," you"," could"," try"," feeding"," your"," dog"," fish"," or"," lamb"," instead",".","\n\n","Try"," Giving"," Your"," Dog"," Hydro","ly","zed"," Protein","\n\n","Hydro","ly","zed"," protein"," is"," another"," option"," for"," dogs"," with"," food"," allergies","."," This"," type"," of"," protein"," is"," broken"," down"," into"," smaller"," molecules"," that"," are"," less"," likely"," to"," trigger"," an"," allergic"," reaction",".","\n\n","Consider"," Making"," Your"," Dog","\u2019","s"," Food"," at"," Home","\n\n","If"," your"," dog"," has"," multiple"," food"," allergies",","," you"," may"," need"," to"," consider"," making"," their"," food"," at"," home","."," This"," can"," help"," ensure"," that"," your"," dog"," is"," getting"," the"," nutrients"," they"," need"," without"," being"," exposed"," to"," allergens",".","\n\n","Vacuum"," Your"," House"," to"," Remove"," Flea"," Eggs","\n\n","Fle","as"," can"," be"," a"," major"," source"," of"," allergens"," for"," dogs"," with"," allergic"," dermatitis","."," To"," reduce"," the"," number"," of"," fleas"," in"," your"," home",","," you"," should"," vacuum"," your"," house"," regularly"," to"," remove"," flea"," eggs"," and"," larvae",".","\n\n","Use"," a"," Flea","-","Killing"," Product"," to"," Remove"," the"," Rest"," of"," the"," Eggs"," From"," Your"," House","\n\n","Once"," you"," have"," vacu","umed"," your"," home",","," you"," should"," use"," a"," flea","-","killing"," product"," to"," remove"," the"," rest"," of"," the"," eggs"," from"," your"," home","."," These"," products"," can"," be"," in"," the"," form"," of"," sprays",","," powders",","," or"," fog","gers",".","\n\n","Wash"," Your"," Pet","\u2019","s"," Bedding"," Each"," Week","\n\n","To"," reduce"," your"," dog","\u2019","s"," exposure"," to"," fleas",","," you"," should"," also"," wash"," their"," bedding"," regularly","."," This"," will"," help"," kill"," any"," fleas"," or"," flea"," eggs"," that"," may"," be"," on"," their"," bedding",".","\n\n","Clean"," Out"," Any"," Other"," Places"," Where"," Your"," Pet"," Sp","ends"," Time","\n\n","In"," addition"," to"," their"," bedding",","," you"," should"," also"," clean"," out"," any"," other"," places"," where"," your"," pet"," spends"," time",","," such"," as"," their"," crate"," or"," favorite"," spot"," on"," the"," couch",".","\n\n","Clear"," Fle","as"," From"," Your"," Pet"],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}